    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This battered yet lovingly polished +1 breastplate is marked by three chipped glass circles set over the heart, each of a different color. Three times per day, the wearer may tap a circle to activate it, enveloping her in a shimmering aura that protects her from harm. The wearer gains DR 10/- and is protected if she were under the effects of a globe of invulnerability spell. The effect ends as soon as the wearer makes an offensive action or casts an offensive spell, or after 1 minute. In addition, whenever the wearer casts a cure spell or administers a cure potion while under this effect, she may add one additional die to the total amount of damage healed.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +1 breastplate</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Magic Arms and Armor, cure light wounds, sanctuary</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Champions Of Purity",
